The paper discusses the wireless industry and its approach towards meeting E2E communication requirements, which falls under the category of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). It also talks about the need for innovation and the involvement of academia, SMEs, industries, and start-ups, which can be categorized under information theory (cs.IT) and cyber security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the need for decentralized mandate-driven intelligence, which can be related to systems and control (cs.SY) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
